  "text": "The ways that made free from grazing of degraded rangeland area to specified period of time and it is highly practiced in different part of Ethiopia .But in the long run it revealed that the proliferation of bush encroachment is a major threat in these enclosures over time, as compared to more regularly grazed rangelands if it is not incorporated scientific and indigenous knowledge [CITATION_1] ).",
